name: User navigate to the Merchant dashboard and click on the merchant accounts then verifying the entire screen
fullName: User navigate to the Merchant dashboard and click on the merchant accounts then verifying the entire screen

steps.name: When user clicks on the Request dropdown
And clicks on the Merchant Accounts tab
Then user should be on the Merchant Accounts page
assert expected **<span.text-base.text-cgy4>** to have text **Merchant Accounts**
And the Merchant Setting button should be disabled for the under review, cancelled, unverified, terminated, declined account
When user clicks on the Merchant Settings Button for the active account
Then the company Information screen should be displayed
assert expected **<p.text-xs.font-bold.CompanyInformation_leftTitle1__5xJEU.text-cm3>** to have text **Company Information**
When User click on the Go to Merchant Button
Then Token Account screen should be displayed for the Active Account
get div[class='MerchantWalletDashboard_account_balance__pQIMG pt-6 px-6 pb-8'] span[class='text-base text-cgy4']
assert expected **<span.text-base.text-cgy4>** to have text **Total Available Funds**
And cancelled screen should be displayed for the cancel account
xpath //div[contains(@class,'icon-small-arrow text-base fill-current hover:text-cm3 false DashboardMenu_downArrow__YA3Vr')]
And Merchant Application tracker screen should be displayed for the unverified Account
assert expected **<p.text-xl.font-bold.leading-5.text-cgy4>** to have text **Merchant Application**
And Terminated screen should be displayed for the terminated account
xpath //div[contains(@class,'icon-small-arrow text-base fill-current hover:text-cm3 false DashboardMenu_downArrow__YA3Vr')]
And Declined screen should be displayed for the Declined account
xpath //div[contains(@class,'icon-small-arrow text-base fill-current hover:text-cm3 false DashboardMenu_downArrow__YA3Vr')]
And Under Review screen should be displayed for the under review account
